Package curam.util.connectors.mqseries

Contains utility classes for connecting to other systems using JMS, such as MQ Series

See:
          Description

Class Summary
MQFieldMapper Handles the mapping of one field within a class to/from an MQSeries string.
MQFieldMapper.BlobMapper Maps a Blob field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.BooleanMapper Maps a boolean field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.ByteMapper Maps a byte field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.CharMapper Maps a char field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.DateMapper Maps a Date field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.DateTimeMapper Maps a DateTime field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.DoubleMapper Maps a double field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.FloatMapper Maps a float field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.IntMapper Maps an int field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.LongMapper Maps a long field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.MoneyMapper Maps a Money field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.ShortMapper Maps a short field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMapper.StringMapper Maps a String field in a struct to/from an MQSeries message.
MQFieldMetadata Contains field meta data to determine how the field should be mapped to/from an MQSeries message.
MQStructMapper Provides functionality for mapping struct classes to/from MQ Series messages.
MQUtils Contains utility classes for the MQSeries Curam connector.
 

Package curam.util.connectors.mqseries Description

Contains utility classes for connecting to other systems using JMS, such as MQ Series.
